description.en:
The MetaONEz is the first-ever fractionalized metaverse bundle which includes properties/lands in Sandbox, Decentraland, Somnium Space and Cryptovoxels.

The Portfolio includes 30 valuable parcels from the Metaverse. The land parcels include connected properties in Sandbox, Decentraland and Somnium Space and all five Cryptovoxel properties are located in top districts in Origin City. It is the first-ever NFT bundle focused on the Metaverse that utilizes Niftex’s fractionalization technology and is available for purchase.
